title: Original Cannoli By BAMS
description: Original Cannoli by Bam’s Cannoli is a key lime cream-filled and cereal covered cannoli flavored e juice that has been a best selling dessert flavor since before 2015. The inhale of Original Cannoli e juice brings forth the tart and sweet key lime filled cannoli flavor that is very similar to the flavor sensation of the real dessert. The exhale brings you the fruity cereal and smooth whipped cream flavor notions pulling this entire experience together into one enjoyable vape hit.Flavor Profile: Key Lime Cannoli, Fruity Cereal, Whipped CreamVG/PG: 70/30Nicotine Level: 0MG, 3MG, 6MGBottle Size: 100ML
